lead_paragraph: Former Guatemalan football federation president Brayan Jimenez was taken to the capital's airport on Tuesday for extradition to the United States to face corruption charges, two local officials said.

headline.print_headline: Guatemala Takes Ex-Football Chief to Airport for U.S. Extradition
